java.lang.Object

ImagePresenter<T>
public static class ImagePresenter.Builder<T>
extends java.lang.Object

A builder for an ImagePresenter.

ImagePresenter.Builder#setImageView(android.widget.ImageView) setImageView, ImagePresenter.Builder#setPathLoader setPathLoader, and ImagePresenter.Builder#setImageLoader setIamgeLoader are required.
